verses.text_plain: The book of the generation of Jesus Christ, the son of David, the son of Abraham.
verses.verse_html: 1The book of the generation of Jesus Christ, the son of David, the son of Abraham.

verses.text_plain: Abraham begat Isaac; and Isaac begat Jacob; and Jacob begat Judas and his brethren;
verses.verse_html: 2Abraham begat Isaac; and Isaac begat Jacob; and Jacob begat Judas and his brethren;

verses.text_plain: And Judas begat Phares and Zara of Thamar; and Phares begat Esrom; and Esrom begat Aram;
verses.verse_html: 3And Judas begat Phares and Zara of Thamar; and Phares begat Esrom; and Esrom begat Aram;

verses.text_plain: And Aram begat Aminadab; and Aminadab begat Naasson; and Naasson begat Salmon;
verses.verse_html: 4And Aram begat Aminadab; and Aminadab begat Naasson; and Naasson begat Salmon;

verses.text_plain: And Salmon begat Booz of Rachab; and Booz begat Obed of Ruth; and Obed begat Jesse;
verses.verse_html: 5And Salmon begat Booz of Rachab; and Booz begat Obed of Ruth; and Obed begat Jesse;

verses.text_plain: And Jesse begat David the king; and David the king begat Solomon of her that had been the wife of Urias;
verses.verse_html: 6And Jesse begat David the king; and David the king begat Solomon of her that had been the wife of Urias;

verses.text_plain: And Solomon begat Roboam; and Roboam begat Abia; and Abia begat Asa;
verses.verse_html: 7And Solomon begat Roboam; and Roboam begat Abia; and Abia begat Asa;

verses.text_plain: And Asa begat Josaphat; and Josaphat begat Joram; and Joram begat Ozias;
verses.verse_html: 8And Asa begat Josaphat; and Josaphat begat Joram; and Joram begat Ozias;

verses.text_plain: And Ozias begat Joatham; and Joatham begat Achaz; and Achaz begat Ezekias;
verses.verse_html: 9And Ozias begat Joatham; and Joatham begat Achaz; and Achaz begat Ezekias;

verses.text_plain: And Ezekias begat Manasses; and Manasses begat Amon; and Amon begat Josias;
verses.verse_html: 10And Ezekias begat Manasses; and Manasses begat Amon; and Amon begat Josias;

verses.text_plain: And Josias begat Jechonias and his brethren, about the time they were carried away to Babylon:
verses.verse_html: 11And Josias begat Jechonias and his brethren, about the time they were carried away to Babylon:

verses.text_plain: And after they were brought to Babylon, Jechonias begat Salathiel; and Salathiel begat Zorobabel;
verses.verse_html: 12And after they were brought to Babylon, Jechonias begat Salathiel; and Salathiel begat Zorobabel;

verses.text_plain: And Zorobabel begat Abiud; and Abiud begat Eliakim; and Eliakim begat Azor;
verses.verse_html: 13And Zorobabel begat Abiud; and Abiud begat Eliakim; and Eliakim begat Azor;

verses.text_plain: And Azor begat Sadoc; and Sadoc begat Achim; and Achim begat Eliud;
verses.verse_html: 14And Azor begat Sadoc; and Sadoc begat Achim; and Achim begat Eliud;

verses.text_plain: And Eliud begat Eleazar; and Eleazar begat Matthan; and Matthan begat Jacob;
verses.verse_html: 15And Eliud begat Eleazar; and Eleazar begat Matthan; and Matthan begat Jacob;

verses.text_plain: And Jacob begat Joseph the husband of Mary, of whom was born Jesus, who is called Christ.
verses.verse_html: 16And Jacob begat Joseph the husband of Mary, of whom was born Jesus, who is called Christ.

verses.text_plain: So all the generations from Abraham to David are fourteen generations; and from David until the carrying away into Babylon are fourteen generations; and from the carrying away into Babylon unto Christ are fourteen generations.
verses.verse_html: 17So all the generations from Abraham to David are fourteen generations; and from David until the carrying away into Babylon are fourteen generations; and from the carrying away into Babylon unto Christ are fourteen generations.

verses.text_plain: Now the birth of Jesus Christ was on this wise: When as his mother Mary was espoused to Joseph, before they came together, she was found with child of the Holy Ghost.
verses.verse_html: 18Now the birth of Jesus Christ was on this wise: When as his mother Mary was espoused to Joseph, before they came together, she was found with child of the Holy Ghost.

tokens.strong_raw: G1722 G1064 G2192 lemma.TR:εν lemma.TR:γαστρι lemma.TR:εχουσα

verses.text_plain: Then Joseph her husband, being a just man, and not willing to make her a publick example, was minded to put her away privily.
verses.verse_html: 19Then Joseph her husband, being a just man, and not willing to make her a publick example, was minded to put her away privily.

verses.text_plain: But while he thought on these things, behold, the angel of the Lord appeared unto him in a dream, saying, Joseph, thou son of David, fear not to take unto thee Mary thy wife: for that which is conceived in her is of the Holy Ghost.
verses.verse_html: 20But while he thought on these things, behold, the angel of the Lord appeared unto him in a dream, saying, Joseph, thou son of David, fear not to take unto thee Mary thy wife: for that which is conceived in her is of the Holy Ghost.

verses.text_plain: And she shall bring forth a son, and thou shalt call his name JESUS: for he shall save his people from their sins.
verses.verse_html: 21And she shall bring forth a son, and thou shalt call his name JESUS: for he shall save his people from their sins.

verses.text_plain: Now all this was done, that it might be fulfilled which was spoken of the Lord by the prophet, saying,
verses.verse_html: 22Now all this was done, that it might be fulfilled which was spoken of the Lord by the prophet, saying,

verses.text_plain: Behold, a virgin shall be with child, and shall bring forth a son, and they shall call his name Emmanuel, which being interpreted is, God with us.
verses.verse_html: 23Behold, a virgin shall be with child, and shall bring forth a son, and they shall call his name Emmanuel, which being interpreted is, God with us.

verses.text_plain: Then Joseph being raised from sleep did as the angel of the Lord had bidden him, and took unto him his wife:
verses.verse_html: 24Then Joseph being raised from sleep did as the angel of the Lord had bidden him, and took unto him his wife:

verses.text_plain: And knew her not till she had brought forth her firstborn son: and he called his name JESUS.
verses.verse_html: 25And knew her not till she had brought forth her firstborn son: and he called his name JESUS.
